15. "The universe is not outside of you. Look inside yourself; everything that you want, you already are."
16. "You were born with wings, why prefer to crawl through life?"
17. "When you let go of who you are, you become who you might be."
18. "Why are you so busy with the worry of what you don’t have? Go find what you have."
19. "The mind is a beautiful servant, but a dangerous master."
20. "Don’t be satisfied with the stories that come before you. Unfold your own myth."

21. "Live life as if everything is rigged in your favor."
22. "Go on! Go on! Take the leap and show yourself."
23. "If you are seeking, seek us with joy. For joy is the gateway to truth."
24. "The soul has been given its own ears to hear things the mind does not understand."
